{"tid":149360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消防局外翻車　消防員衝出搶救　交警趕赴途中自炒","createTime":"2017-03-09T08:38:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T15:14:02.000Z","uid":5195,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bb4bb44ffb2b493c19b04818dd42ce7c8c6944d9","tid":149360,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T08:38:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.hk01.com/article/76706\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F76706&d=0fhT0ZiErqSmjIt08Df9or%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=bb4c6112\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hk01.com/article/76706</a><br />\n<br />\n今早11時許，一輛白色私家車沿柴灣常安街行駛，惟駕駛期間疑汽車失控，撞向路邊鐵欄失事翻側，剛好擱在行人路旁，並橫亘柴灣消防局門外，私家車司機及乘客一度受傷被困車中。消防員及救護員在局內得見狀，立即跑出局外參與救援。多名消防員更合力將私家車扶穩，拯救傷者，其後兩人救出，即時送往東區醫院治理，交通警員到場調查意外成因。<br />\n<br />\n另一輛接報前赴處理私家車交通意外警員，沿柴灣盛泰道行駛，在路中突失控跣低，警員跌在地上，駕駛人士見狀報警，救護車到場，將受傷警員送院。"},{"pid":"81834a836997e5c1cdfdb76e3d3f4c181345ea54","tid":149360,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T08:41:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.clipartfest.com/371d2c744130eb9c88242b0bece7e27e_laughing-face-clip-art-free-clipart-laughing-face_1600-1207.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.clipartfest.com%2F371d2c744130eb9c88242b0bece7e27e_laughing-face-clip-art-free-clipart-laughing-face_1600-1207.jpeg&h=d4eda5c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e3f7eaa0d5957070615f5cde463e2328c5c9e205","tid":149360,"uid":87591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T08:44:11.000Z","msg":"好撚邪"},{"pid":"108265e93b6c780f079b126bf0e13a6144d9ad29","tid":149360,"uid":17611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T08:46:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/09/164621_0f9be3976cbca520d2085aafa42e341b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F09%2F164621_0f9be3976cbca520d2085aafa42e341b.jpg&h=5882eb43&s